{"text_id":235109,"tokens":["The"," act"," of"," decision","-","making",","," especially"," when"," confronting"," significant"," life"," choices",","," can"," be"," both"," a"," daunting"," and"," crucial"," endeavor","."," It"," is"," a"," process"," where"," the"," merits"," of"," collective"," wisdom"," cannot"," be"," underestimated","."," I"," firmly"," believe"," in"," the"," importance"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," when"," making"," pivotal"," decisions",","," as"," doing"," so"," can"," provide"," diverse"," insights",","," identify"," potential"," biases",","," and"," ultimately"," lead"," to"," more"," informed"," and"," effective"," outcomes",".","\n","The"," diversity"," of"," perspectives"," is"," one"," of"," the"," most"," compelling"," reasons"," to"," seek"," advice"," widely","."," Each"," individual","'","s"," life"," experiences"," shape"," their"," outlook",","," enabling"," them"," to"," see"," different"," angles"," of"," the"," same"," problem","."," For"," instance",","," when"," deciding"," on"," a"," career"," move",","," advice"," from"," various"," colleagues",","," mentors",","," and"," industry"," connections"," can"," unearth"," considerations"," like"," market"," trends",","," personal"," growth"," opportunities",","," and"," potential"," risks"," that"," a"," singular"," viewpoint"," might"," miss","."," When"," I"," was"," at"," a"," crossroads"," in"," my"," career",","," it"," was"," the"," combined"," counsel"," of"," a"," former"," professor",","," a"," close"," friend",","," and"," an"," industry"," mentor"," that"," helped"," me"," see"," beyond"," immediate"," gains"," towards"," long","-","term"," satisfaction"," and"," professional"," development",".","\n","Furthermore",","," consultation"," can"," act"," as"," a"," safeguard"," against"," personal"," biases"," and"," blind"," spots","."," Humans"," are"," prone"," to"," cognitive"," biases","\u2014","such"," as"," confirmation"," bias",",","